    10 │ 
    11 │ 
    12 │ 
    13 │ ## Endpoints
    14 │ 
    15 │ - `GET /api/users` — List all users
    16 │ - `POST /api/users` — Create a new user
    17 │ - `GET /api/health` — Health check
    18 │ 
    19 │ ## Running
    20 │ 
    21 │ ```bash
    22 │ sbt run
    23 │ ```
    24 │ 
    25 │ ## Architecture
    26 │ 
    27 │ The app uses a simple controller pattern. Each route maps to a handler function
    28 │ that takes a `Request` and returns a `Response`.
    29 │ 
